flowRoot.flowPara: System requirements: This operating system will run in most modern PCs with at least 1 GB of RAM and 5 GB of disk space.

openSUSE® 13.2 is a powerful and free Linux based operating system for your computer. Surf the web, work on documents while listening to music, set up a server or desktop computer. The choice is yours and you‘ll have a lot of fun!

The openSUSE project, a worldwide community that promotes the use of Linux everywhere, creates this Linux distribution in an open and transparent way as part of the global Free and Open Source Software movement.

This DVD includes everything you need to get your desktop, laptop or server up and running with Linux. You can also take 13.2 for a test drive before you install it. Just boot your computer from this DVD.
